This model is created by merging many LoRa and other models to produce pictures of cute furry girls. I hope you like it. (*^▽^*)

融合了一些模型和Lora得到的模型，可以生产可爱福瑞图。希望各位用得开心。(*^▽^*)

Recommend settings:

512×768, DPM++ 2M Karras, Steps: 20-30, and add “furry, animal ears, tail, " to prompt.

Used models:

NineKeyMIX5

Mistoon_Anime

MIX-HIRES
Used Loras:

Furry girl
